'''颶風雷蒙德'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Raymond}}）是2013年東太平洋唯一的[[熱帶氣旋等級|大型颶風]]，並短暫威脅[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]西南部沿岸，然後再度返回大海。[[2013年太平洋颶風季|2013年太平洋颶風季]]的第17個[[熱帶氣旋命名|被命名]]的風暴和第8場颶風，雷蒙德在10月20日從[[墨西哥|墨西哥]][[阿卡普尔科|阿卡普尔科]]以南部的熱帶浪潮發展而成。在熱帶氣旋發展的有利條件下，雷蒙德迅速增強，在{{link-en|熱帶氣旋發展學|Tropical cyclogenesis|形成}}後一天就先後達到[[热带风暴|热带风暴]]和颶風強度。10月21日，颶風達到風力時速205公里的最高強度。一個[[高壓脊|高壓脊]]阻擋颶風前進並迫使其轉向西南方向移動，同時雷蒙德開始因[[风切变|风切变]]而迅速減弱。第二天，熱帶氣旋減弱至熱帶風暴標準。在向西移動後，雷蒙德重新進入較有利的條件，它可以在10月27日向北轉向重新增強至颶風強度。數小時後，颶風達到風力時速165公里的第二次最高強度。惡劣的大氣條件導致雷蒙德最後一次減弱，10月30日，[[國家颶風中心|國家颶風中心]]宣布熱帶氣旋已經消散。

== 氣象歷史 ==
{{storm path|Raymond 2013 track.png}}
2013年10月17日，[[中美洲|中美洲]]附近有大範圍[[低气压|低氣壓區]]，與其關聯的對流雜亂無章，這片不穩定的天氣區域便是颶風雷蒙德的前身<ref>{{cite web|author=Christopher W. Landsea|title=Graphical Tropical Weather Outlook|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/epac/201310171743/index.php?basin=epac&current_issuance=201310171743|publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration|work=National Hurricane Center|date=2013-10-17|accessdate=2013-10-27|archive-date=2015-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151022212012/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/epac/201310171743/index.php?basin=epac&current_issuance=201310171743|dead-url=no}}</ref>。系統向西至西北偏西移動，預計環境條件有利於熱帶氣旋發展。相應地，[[國家颶風中心|國家颶風中心]]認為該系統有中等程度的可能性在五天內成為熱帶氣旋<ref>{{cite web|author=Michael J. Brennan|title=Graphical Tropical Weather Outlook|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/epac/201310180500/index.php?basin=epac&current_issuance=201310180500|publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration|work=National Hurricane Center|date=2013-10-17|accessdate=2013-10-27|archive-date=2015-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151024055357/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/epac/201310180500/index.php?basin=epac&current_issuance=201310180500|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在隨後的48小時內，低氣壓的中心變得更加明確，對流活動穩步增加和變得有組織，促使國家颶風中心提高系統在五天內成為熱帶氣旋的可能性至高<ref>{{cite web|author=John P. Cangialosi|title=Graphical Tropical Weather Outlook|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/epac/201310191126/index.php?basin=epac&current_issuance=201310191126|publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration|work=National Hurricane Center|date=2013-10-19|accessdate=2013-10-27|archive-date=2016-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160411120625/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/epac/201310191126/index.php?basin=epac&current_issuance=201310191126|dead-url=no}}</ref>。10月19日上午，該系統轉向西北移動並繼續發展；經衛星強度估計和衛星圖像的證實，這個擾動在UTC凌晨0時被升格為第十七{{lang|en|E}}號熱帶低氣壓<ref name="TCR">{{cite report|author=Robbie Berg|title=Tropical Cyclone Report: Hurricane Raymond|url={{NHC TCR url|id=EP172013_Raymond}}|publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration|work=National Hurricane Center|date=2014-01-06|accessdate=2017-06-26|format=PDF|location=Miami, Florida}}</ref>。儘管雲頂逐漸回暖，但低氣壓的整體雲層格局在第二天早上有所改善，隨後在UTC上午6時將其升級為熱帶風暴，並以“雷蒙德”（{{lang|en|Raymond}}）命名<ref name="TCR"/>。此時，氣旋位於[[墨西哥|墨西哥]][[阿卡普尔科|阿卡普尔科]]西南偏南約300公里<ref>{{cite report|author=Lixion A. Avila|title=Tropical Storm Raymond Public Advisory Number 2|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep17/ep172013.public.002.shtml|work=National Hurricane Center|publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration|date=2013-10-20|accessdate=2013-10-27|archive-date=2016-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160402132431/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep17/ep172013.public.002.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

獲得命名後，雷蒙德繼續變得更有組織。深層對流在環流中心繼續增加，而微波圖像則指出了內核心的形成階段<ref>{{cite report|author=Michael J. Brennan|title=Tropical Storm Raymond Discussion Number 3|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep17/ep172013.discus.003.shtml|work=National Hurricane Center|publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration|date=2013-10-20|accessdate=2013-10-27|archive-date=2020-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029113258/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep17/ep172013.discus.003.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此後不久，系統開始一個[[快速增强|快速增强]]的時期，被國家颶風中心預報員描述為“驚人”和“令人印象深刻”<ref name="Cat2Raymond">{{cite report|author=Daniel P. Brown|title=Hurricane Raymond Discussion Number 5|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep17/ep172013.discus.005.shtml|work=National Hurricane Center|publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration|date=2013-10-20|accessdate=2013-10-27|archive-date=2020-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031053301/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep17/ep172013.discus.005.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。UTC10月21日凌晨0時，雷蒙德獲升級為一級颶風<ref name="TCR"/>；6小時後，由於可見光和紅外衛星圖像上的小而明確的眼睛變得明顯，因此它獲升級為二級颶風<ref name="Cat2Raymond"/><ref>{{cite report|author=Robbie J. Berg|author2=Daniel P. Brown|title=Hurricane Raymond Intermediate Advisory Number 4A|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep17/ep172013.public_a.004.shtml|work=National Hurricane Center|publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration|date=2013-10-20|accessdate=2013-10-27|archive-date=2020-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031101736/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep17/ep172013.public_a.004.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。結合衛星強度估計，颶風獲升級為大型颶風—在[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]達到第三級或以上—使雷蒙德成為[[2013年太平洋颶風季|2013年太平洋颶風季]]的首個大型颶風，也是2013年西半球的首個大型颶風<ref name="TCR"/><ref>{{cite report|author=John P. Cangialosi|author2=Lixion A. Avila|title=Hurricane Raymond Discussion Number 6|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep17/ep172013.discus.006.shtml|work=National Hurricane Center|publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration|date=2013-10-21|accessdate=2013-10-27|archive-date=2020-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028170142/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep17/ep172013.discus.006.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Lindsay Milbourne|title=Tropical Storm Lorenzo forms in central Atlantic-no threat; Raymond a major hurricane near southwest Mexico|url=http://blog.myfoxhurricane.com/2013/10/21/tropical-depression-13-forms-in-central-atlantic-no-threat-raymond-a-major-hurricane-near-southwest-mexico|publisher=myFOX Hurricane|work=myFOX hurricane|date=2013-10-21|accessdate=2013-10-27|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131026020853/http://blog.myfoxhurricane.com/2013/10/21/tropical-depression-13-forms-in-central-atlantic-no-threat-raymond-a-major-hurricane-near-southwest-mexico/|archivedate=2013-10-26}}</ref>。系統停止不動後，雷蒙德進行[[眼牆置換循環|眼牆置換循環]]，導致其增強趨勢暫時停止。不過到了10月21日下午，系統在組織上有所增加和變得更加對稱，其風眼溫度上升。UTC下午18時，雷蒙德達到最高強度，[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]為每小時205公里，最低氣壓為951毫巴（百帕; 28.08英寸汞柱）<ref name="TCR"/>。此後，西南的垂直風切變增加，導致系統開始減弱趨勢。UTC10月22日上午6時，雷蒙德被降格為二級颶風<ref name="TCR"/>。那天下午，一架空軍颶風獵人飛機的數據顯示，該系統比預測還要弱，只達一級颶風的下限<ref name="TCR"/><ref>{{cite report|author=Michael J. Brennan|title=Hurricane Raymond Discussion Number 12|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep17/ep172013.discus.012.shtml|work=National Hurricane Center|publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration|date=2013-10-21|accessdate=2013-10-27|archive-date=2020-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028055149/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep17/ep172013.discus.012.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。沿着[[下加利福尼亞半島|下加利福尼亞半島]]附近的一個高壓脊的南部轉向西南偏西移動，雷蒙德在UTC上午6時減弱為熱帶風暴<ref name="TCR"/>。

[[File:Raymond_Oct_27_2013_2115Z.jpg|thumb]]
10月23日，持續的風切變導致低層中心暴露在大範圍的雲層，表示乾燥的空氣，填滿了熱帶氣旋混亂的西半圓<ref>{{cite report|author=Eric S. Blake|title=Tropical Storm Raymond Discussion Number 16|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep17/ep172013.discus.016.shtml|work=National Hurricane Center|publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration|date=2013-10-23|accessdate=2013-10-27|archive-date=2017-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170702183234/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep17/ep172013.discus.016.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。第二天，中心發生了深層的驟雨和雷暴活動；然而，沒有注意到強度的變化<ref>{{cite report|author=Eric S. Blake|title=Tropical Storm Raymond Discussion Number 20|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep17/ep172013.discus.020.shtml|work=National Hurricane Center|publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration|date=2013-10-24|accessdate=2013-10-27|archive-date=2020-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028132703/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep17/ep172013.discus.020.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。隨著風切變方向轉到東南方，上層流出開始逐漸擴大<ref>{{cite report|author=Lixion A. Avila|title=Tropical Storm Raymond Discussion Number 21|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep17/ep172013.discus.021.shtml|work=National Hurricane Center|publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration|date=2013-10-24|accessdate=2013-10-27|archive-date=2020-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031230130/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep17/ep172013.discus.021.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。儘管預測風暴將會增強，雷蒙德在接下來的48小時內的強度變化不大，也許是中等溫度異常溫暖的結果<ref>{{cite report|author=Christopher W. Landsea|title=Tropical Storm Raymond Discussion Number 27|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep17/ep172013.discus.027.shtml|work=National Hurricane Center|publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration|date=2013-10-26|accessdate=2013-10-27|archive-date=2017-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170702183510/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep17/ep172013.discus.027.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而，到10月29日晚上，低層中心深層對流開始發展，對流帶逐漸增加<ref>{{cite report|author=Todd B. Kimberlain|title=Tropical Storm Raymond Discussion Number 29|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep17/ep172013.discus.029.shtml|work=National Hurricane Center|publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration|date=2013-10-26|accessdate=2013-10-27|archive-date=2020-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028185118/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep17/ep172013.discus.029.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。UTC10月27日中午12時，雲層實況轉變為中心密集雲團，而微波圖像則可以看見風眼；結合衛星強度估計，雷蒙德再次升格為一級颶風，此時氣旋位於下加利福尼亞半島最南方西南偏南約1,165公里<ref name="TCR"/>。10月28日早上，雷蒙德達到風力時速165公里，氣壓971毫巴（百帕，28.67英寸汞柱）的第二波最高強度，已經發展出一個雲塞風眼和一個中心密集雲團<ref name="TCR"/><ref>{{cite report|author=Todd Kimberlain|title=Hurricane Raymond Discussion Number 33|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep17/ep172013.discus.033.shtml?|work=National Hurricane Center|publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration|date=2013-10-28|accessdate=2013-11-01|archive-date=2020-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028134629/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep17/ep172013.discus.033.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。10月29日早上，風切變的增加擾亂了對流，使颶風回落到熱帶風暴標準<ref name="TCR"/>。雖然當天的雷暴短暫增加<ref>{{cite report|author=Daniel P. Brown|title=Tropical Storm Raymond Discussion Number 38|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep17/ep172013.discus.038.shtml?|work=National Hurricane Center|publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration|date=2013-10-29|accessdate=2013-11-01|archive-date=2020-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031102129/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep17/ep172013.discus.038.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>，持續的風切變使風暴進一步減弱<ref>{{cite report|author=Jack Beven|title=Tropical Storm Raymond Discussion Number 41|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep17/ep172013.discus.041.shtml?|work=National Hurricane Center|publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration|date=2013-10-30|accessdate=2013-11-01|archive-date=2020-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028055358/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep17/ep172013.discus.041.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。因為環流已經逐漸拉長，並脱離至對流之外，雷蒙德於10月30日減弱至熱帶低氣壓標準<ref name="TCR"/><ref>{{cite report|author=Daniel P. Brown|title=Tropical Depression Raymond Discussion Number 42|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep17/ep172013.discus.042.shtml?|work=National Hurricane Center|publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration|date=2013-10-30|accessdate=2013-11-01|archive-date=2017-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170702183854/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep17/ep172013.discus.042.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。那天晚上，低氣壓退化成殘留低氣壓區<ref name="TCR"/><ref>{{cite report|author=Robbie Berg|title=Post-Tropical Cyclone Raymond Discussion Number 43|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep17/ep172013.discus.043.shtml?|work=National Hurricane Center|publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration|date=2013-10-30|accessdate=2013-11-01|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101074002/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep17/ep172013.discus.043.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在接下來的兩天裡，雷蒙德的殘留向西慢慢轉向，在11月1日早上消散<ref name="TCR"/>。

==防災措施和影響==
由於雷蒙德的威脅，[[格雷羅州|格雷羅州]]和[[米卻肯州|米卻肯州]]的部分地區接獲“橙色”警報，並且大部分[[科利馬州|科利馬州]]和[[哈利斯科州|哈利斯科州]]發出了“黃色”警報<ref>{{Es icon}} {{cite news|title=En alerta roja por Raymond, Guerrero y Michoacán|url=http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/huracan-raymond-alerta-michoacan-guerrero-clases-959676.html|accessdate=2013-10-21|newspaper=El Universal|date=2013-10-21|archive-date=2013-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131025232502/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/huracan-raymond-alerta-michoacan-guerrero-clases-959676.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
{{link-en|哥斯達格蘭德|Costa Grande}}港口所有小船和體育活動取消<ref name=EU1>{{Es icon}} {{cite news|title=Raymond podría convertirse en huracán esta noche|url=http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/raymond-huracan-guerrero-959588.html|accessdate=2013-10-20|newspaper=[[El_Universal_(Mexico_City)|El Universal]]|date=2013-10-20|archive-date=2014-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140228033607/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/raymond-huracan-guerrero-959588.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[曼萨尼约|曼萨尼约]]港被命令於10月21日關閉<ref name=EU6>{{Es icon}} {{cite news|title=Colima permanece en alerta por huracán Raymond|url=http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/colima-alerta-raymond-959758.html|accessdate=2013-10-21|newspaper=El Universal|date=2013-10-21|archive-date=2014-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140908014804/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/colima-alerta-raymond-959758.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。格雷羅州州長{{link-en|墨西哥目前州長名單|List of current Mexican state governors|安赫爾·阿吉雷·里維羅}}向該州9個市政府宣布進入[[紧急状态|紧急状态]]，而81個毗鄰颶風的市鎮的居民要求從容易有水災地區疏散<ref name=EU2>{{Es icon}} {{cite news|title=Por Raymond, pide Aguirre emergencia para 9 municipios|url=http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/por-raymond-pide-aguirre-emergencia-para-9-municipios-959605.html|accessdate=2013-10-20|newspaper=El Universal|date=2013-10-20|archive-date=2014-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140223000852/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/por-raymond-pide-aguirre-emergencia-para-9-municipios-959605.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=AP1>{{Es icon}}{{cite web|title=‘Raymond’ incrementa su fuerza y ya es huracán categoría 2|url=http://www.animalpolitico.com/2013/10/raymond-ya-es-huracan-categoria-1|publisher=Animal Politico|date=2013-10-20|accessdate=2013-10-21|archive-date=2020-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200906235021/https://www.animalpolitico.com/2013/10/raymond-ya-es-huracan-categoria-1/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。約25個庇護所開放<ref name=EU10 />；官員從這些收容所撤離了400多人<ref name=EU3>{{Es icon}}{{cite news|title=Aplican plan DNIII por el huracán Raymond en Gro.|url=http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/raymond-se-acerca-a-mexico-con-categoria-3-959643.html|accessdate=2013-10-21|newspaper=El Universal|date=2013-10-21|archive-date=2014-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140227092905/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/raymond-se-acerca-a-mexico-con-categoria-3-959643.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，包括在[[阿卡普尔科|阿卡普尔科]]附近的100人<ref name=DG>{{Es icon}} {{cite news|title=Call Aguirre to take precautions, to the strengthening of Hurricane "Raymond"|url=http://www.diariodeguerrero.com.mx/incio/pagina-principal/9248-llama-aguirre-a-tomar-precauciones-ante-el-fortalecimiento-del-huracan-raymond.html|accessdate=2013-10-22|newspaper=Dary of Guerrero|date=2013-10-22|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131023055443/http://www.diariodeguerrero.com.mx/incio/pagina-principal/9248-llama-aguirre-a-tomar-precauciones-ante-el-fortalecimiento-del-huracan-raymond.html|archivedate=2013-10-23}}</ref>。
在系統到達之前，約有3000名軍人被運送<ref name=EU9>{{Es icon}} {{cite news|title=Despliegan a 3 mil soldados en Gro. por Raymond|url=http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/guerrero-alerta-huracan-reymond-soldados-959759.html|accessdate=2013-10-21|newspaper=El Universal|date=2013-10-21|archive-date=2014-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140227051419/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/guerrero-alerta-huracan-reymond-soldados-959759.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。阿卡普爾科以西大部分沿海社區的學校和班級都關閉，包括[[锡瓦塔内霍|锡瓦塔内霍]]<ref name=Yahoo!>{{cite news|title=Raymond becomes major hurricane as it nears Mexico|url=https://news.yahoo.com/raymond-becomes-major-hurricane-nears-mexico-091659556.html|date=2013-10-21|publisher=Yahoo News|accessdate=2013-10-21|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305072349/http://news.yahoo.com/raymond-becomes-major-hurricane-nears-mexico-091659556.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。僅在格雷羅州，有10個市政府暫停上課<ref>{{Es icon}} {{cite news|title=Guerrero suspende clases en 10 municipios|url=http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/guerrero-suspende-clases-en-10-municipios-959620.html|accessdate=2013-10-21|newspaper=El Universal|date=2013-10-20|archive-date=2013-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131026063534/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/guerrero-suspende-clases-en-10-municipios-959620.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而在整個米卻肯州，課程也被暫停<ref name=EU8>{{Es icon}} {{cite news|title=Michoacán, en sesión permanente por Raymond|url=http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/huracan-raymond-michoacan-959721.html|accessdate=2013-10-21|newspaper=El Universal|date=2013-10-21|archive-date=2014-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222215309/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/huracan-raymond-michoacan-959721.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

兩天內，阿卡普爾科附近錄得194毫米的最高雨量<ref name=LJ>{{cite news |title=Hurricane Raymond weakens near Mexico |url=http://www.lansingstatejournal.com/usatoday/article/3142927 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20131023141122/http://www.lansingstatejournal.com/usatoday/article/3142927 |dead-url=yes |archive-date=2013-10-23 |accessdate=2013-10-22 |newspaper=Langiston Journal |date=2013-10-22 |author=Doyle Rice |author2=USA Today |agency=Associated Press }}</ref>。10月21日，颶風雷蒙德的外圍[[雨帶|雨帶]]為墨西哥沿岸帶來大雨，導致輕微的水災<ref name=EU7>{{Es icon}} {{cite news|title=Evacuan colonias de Acapulco por huracán Raymond|url=http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/acapulco-evacuacion-huracan-raymond-959710.html|accessdate=2013-10-21|newspaper=El Universal|date=2013-10-21|archive-date=2015-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150101160634/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/acapulco-evacuacion-huracan-raymond-959710.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。共有21所房屋被水淹沒，5人需要撤離。有3棵樹倒下，2面牆倒塌<ref name=EUM>{{Es icon}} {{cite news|title=Suspenden búsqueda en La Pintada por Raymond|url=http://m.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/estados/2013/pintada-lluvias-raymond-acapulco-960082.html|accessdate=2013-10-22|newspaper=El Universal minor|date=2013-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029192115/http://m.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/estados/2013/pintada-lluvias-raymond-acapulco-960082.html|archive-date=2013-10-29|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。此外，有585人無家可歸<ref name=EU10>{{Es icon}} {{cite news|title=Fonden para 11 municipios tras Raymond; reanudan clases|url=http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/reanudan-labores-guerrero-960163.html|accessdate=2013-10-22|newspaper=El Universal|date=2013-10-22|archive-date=2013-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131111031144/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/reanudan-labores-guerrero-960163.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。阿卡普爾科的一些街道關閉<ref>{{Es icon}} {{cite news|title=Huracán Raymond descarga lluvias en Guerrero|url=http://www.ultra.com.mx/noticias/guerrero/Nacional/25764-huracan-raymond-descarga-lluvias-en-guerrero.html|accessdate=2013-10-22|newspaper=Ultra|date=2013-10-22|archive-date=2017-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170113165137/http://www.ultra.com.mx/noticias/guerrero/Nacional/25764-huracan-raymond-descarga-lluvias-en-guerrero.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由於雷蒙德的影響，格雷羅州的10個市政府宣佈進入緊急狀態<ref name=EU10 />。

